products.description: The VR rebellion continues with the ROG Strix RX 580 O8G Gaming graphics card. Outshine the competition with ASUS Aura Sync RGB lighting while the industry-first MaxContact technology provides improved thermal transfer with twice the GPU contact. GPU Tweak II and Fan Connect II enable intuitive system monitoring and cooling performance.
